title: Trendemoller 3/31: Trans Day of Visibility, Kaitlin Jenner, Nipsey Hu$$le, Devin Nunes, Skippy, Chris Rock
itunes:title: Trendemoller 3/31: Trans Day of Visibility, Kaitlin Jenner, Nipsey Hu$$le, Devin Nunes, Skippy, Chris Rock
description:
In this edition of Trendemoller, Miles and super producer Becca discuss the Trans Day of Visibility, Fox News hiring Kaitlin Jenner as a contributor, the 3 year anniversary of Nipsey Hu$$le's death, Devin Nunes' terrible decision become head of digital for Truth Social, Skippy recalling peanut butter due to intestine-shredding shards of steel, and Chris Rock 'still processing' that slap.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
